{
  "stem": "15938.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything become like underground.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You weren't allowed to show that if you did have something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember hurrying the prayers in shul and getting home quickly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it wasn't-- compared it wasn't that bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At the time, it felt bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was a lot doing in this town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It became a big busy town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody in town was busy with the soldiers, with coming and people coming from out of town to find people, because a lot of them got shot on the way in or died or perished.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took-- you know, like we were the center in the middle of the town kind of.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they used to come and ask and find and look for these people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I still remember that they were allowed, for instance, those few very Orthodox soldiers, so-called-- they weren't soldiers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They weren't an army.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were working--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Laborers in the army.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's called the Jewish army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were still allowed to take to the barracks kosher food, which I think looking back on it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did allow that, so it wasn't so 100%.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were-- I remember we had about 30, 40 soldiers for seder one-- I think it was the last seder.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was-- you know, it was quite-- quite something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- for us children, it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all these handsome-- they still wore uniform, most of them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the-- I can't say the food was very wonderful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was potatoes on potatoes on potatoes, this different color, different shape, and different size.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We managed a bit of chicken soup.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We managed a matzah, which was all homemade, kind of.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was enough food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, we managed.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
